Package: lpdidcsa
Title: Local Projections DiD and Callaway-Sant'Anna Event Studies
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Olivier", "Godechot", email = "olivier.godechot@sciencespo.fr",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements the Local Projections Difference-in-Differences
    (LP-DiD) estimator of Dube, Girardi, Jorda and Taylor (2025) and a
    local-projection version of the Callaway and Sant'Anna (2021)
    heterogeneity-robust event study estimator. Provides data preparation
    (lpdidcsa_data) and estimation (lpdidcsa) functions, with support for
    absorbing and non-absorbing treatments, inverse probability weighting,
    and reweighting for equally-weighted average treatment effects.
